text: Wolfgang Müller (born 6 October 1931) is a German equestrian. He competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics and the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:German male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of East Germany Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Gorzów Wielkopolski
